{"tid":745380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"的士酒店衝落石級 行家職員有愛推車","createTime":"2018-07-16T16:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T19:44:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"197010b4d23ea1a35afb17b0cf858acbf0275233","tid":745380,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T16:46:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180716/20451529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180716%2F20451529&d=wCT9IhKfBwynynUE1NkBa9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=db67051f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180716%2F20451529&h=108d064c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180716/20451529</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月16日 <br />\n<br />\n的士酒店衝落石級<br />\n行家職員有愛推車<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】紅磡海逸君綽酒店，前晚11時許，一輛的士接載乘客到酒店後空載離開，70多歲司機疑行錯路，駛上行人路及衝落梯級，前輪擱於梯級間，幸司機沒有受傷。<br />\n<br />\n其間4至5名的士同行及酒店職員合力推車，司機入後波終將車駛回路面。職員登記司機資料後，司機將的士駛走。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n旺角上車油麻地落　兩男搭的士使「假大牛」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n醉男爬欄過路失手　捱駛至的士撞重創"},{"pid":"dcc92812768664b8315a2aa9c94dacd69df47d49","tid":745380,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T18:51:36.000Z","msg":"又係紅磡海逸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180216/large/1518749631_6222.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180216%2Flarge%2F1518749631_6222.jpg&h=fb5772ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15745368354f6c22f9462fb4eb2c2f45577b0560","tid":745380,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T19:42:45.000Z","msg":"唔怪得去食buffet <br />\n佢話佢幫我泊車同拎車啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4640e3ee8e826b5d52b92a6ecd59e74922245fa5","tid":745380,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T19:44:35.000Z","msg":"sky哥哥發動升壓渦"}]}